Firefox d yiwen yiminig ɣef web ay yellan d aseɣẓan ilelli. Yetteddu deg Mac OS X, Windows neɣ Linux u yeɛjeb-asen xilla i medden.

Firefox extension neɣ isiɣzaf n Firefox d ihallen tzemreḍ ad ternuḍ i Firefox. Yerna llan aṭas n yisiɣzaf.

Dɣa, yal yiwen yezmer ad ibeddel Firefox ama d udem-is (sɣur yiwen usentel) ama d ihallen ay yernun azal (md. tafeggagt n yifecka, imawalen, tanefilt, atg)

D yiwen wallal s way-s yezmer yiwen ad ibeddel tutlayt n Firefox. Ihi, ma nebɣa ula d nekni nezmer ad t-id-nerr s teqbaylit!

Ugar isalen deg useɣwen https://addons.mozilla.org/fr/firefox/
